  Purpose:     
  Parameters:  <none>
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
    GET FIRST {&BROWSE-NAME}.  
    RUN adecomm/_setcurs.p("WAIT":U).   
    DO WHILE AVAILABLE  _U:     
